main: ^Reyes! It’s been a while, huh? How is it? Being back home?
^Yeah, uh… do you have some time to spare? I need a bit of time away from home right now.
^Of course! Do you want to chat over some coffee?
^Sure, why not. But... I'm worried people will stare at us.
^I mean, I definitely look super trans, haha.
^I mean, yeah, but the way they stare at ME makes me feel very weird.
^I guess it’s because we’re walking together? Don’t worry too much. People always do that to people they think are strange.
^I dunno, Harper. It feels... different, somehow.
^Sorry. I didn't mean to get weird about this. Forget that I brought it up.
